creating a directory
mkdir git-assignment 


navigating to the creatd directory  
cd git-assignment


creating 3 files
touch log.txt code.txt output.txt


initializing the git to track the files
git init 


adding the files to staging area
git add code.txt output.txt


commiting the staged files
git commit -m "assignment 1"


pushing the commiting files to the git respository
git push -u origin master

